      <%= image_tag("form.svg", class: "w-12", alt: "Form icon") %>
      Fill out our online adoption application form.</li>
    <li class="flex items-center gap-x-4">
      <%= image_tag("interview.svg", class: "w-12", alt: "Interview icon") %>
